<FIRST>u a AM-ChemicalSpill     08-08 0406</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Chemical Spill,0416</SECOND>
<HEAD>Derailment Causes Spill, Evacuation</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MIDDLETON, Ga. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
