<HEAD>Britain</HEAD>
<TEXT>
 The Times -LRB- <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> -RRB- The <ORGANIZATION> Sunday </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Times </ORGANIZATION> -LRB- <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> -RRB- The Sun -LRB- <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> -RRB- News of the World -LRB- <LOCATION> London </LOCATION> -RRB-
</TEXT>
