federal budget and empowering the president with the line-item veto. The <ORGANIZATION> GOP </ORGANIZATION> platform committee has been gathering testimony around the country since the end of March. The committee will formally vote on the platform it drafts next Monday, then present it the next day to the full convention for approval.
