<TEXT>
 The trendiest carpet colors this year are white, gray and beige, says <PERSON> Axel </PERSON> <PERSON> Venn </PERSON>, color consultant for <ORGANIZATION> ICI </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Fibres </ORGANIZATION>. He says they combine well with soft, `` cosmetics-influenced hues'' that he says will be the color palette for the'90s. <PERSON> Venn </PERSON> says light colors are popular now because of new carpeting resistance to staining and soiling.
